"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US has sent 3,500 personnel to the region with the USS Tripoli. Israel has targeted command centers in Tehran. The conflict in Iran has been going on for a month, and Trump's approach is not working well, according to the BBC's international editor.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Sends Troops to Region\",            \"translated_version\": \"Estados Unidos ha enviado 3,500 personas a la regi\u00f3n con el USS Tripoli. Israel ha atacado centros de mando en Teher\u00e1n. El conflicto en Ir\u00e1n lleva un mes, y la forma de Trump no est\u00e1 funcionando bien, seg\u00fan el editor internacional de la BBC.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EEUU Env\u00eda Tropas a la Regi\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Israeli military has confirmed that it killed Ali Shoeib, who was associated with Hezbollah's Al Manar TV.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Military Confirms Killing\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito israel\u00ed ha confirmado que mat\u00f3 a Ali Shoeib, quien estaba asociado con la TV Al Manar de Hezbollah.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ej\u00e9rcito Israel\u00ed Confirma Muerte\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"In Kenya, there is a new trend of collecting ants, which has caught the country by surprise. Smugglers are trying to make money from this craze.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ant Collecting Trend in Kenya\",            \"translated_version\": \"En Kenia, hay una nueva moda de recoger hormigas, lo que ha sorprendido al pa\u00eds. Los contrabandistas est\u00e1n tratando de ganar dinero con esta moda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Moda de Hormigas en Kenia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Poor weather and a lack of food and water have led to deaths, according to the Greek coastguard.\",            \"english_title\": \"Deaths Due to Bad Weather\",            \"translated_version\": \"El mal tiempo y la falta de comida y agua han causado muertes, seg\u00fan la guardia costera griega.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muertes por Mal Tiempo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"With the world focused on the war in Iran, there is growing uncertainty about the future of Gaza. Jawad Younes and his uncle Ragheb were buried on Saturday after their family compound was hit the day before.\",            \"english_title\": \"Uncertainty in Gaza\",            \"translated_version\": \"Con el mundo enfocado en la guerra en Ir\u00e1n, hay m\u00e1s incertidumbre sobre el futuro de Gaza. Jawad Younes y su t\u00edo Ragheb fueron enterrados el s\u00e1bado despu\u00e9s de que su casa familiar fuera atacada el d\u00eda anterior.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incertidumbre en Gaza\"        }    ]}"